{"tid":221580,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[技能發動]喺頭頂捉到隻螳螂","createTime":"2017-04-28T20:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T13:59:39.000Z","uid":12941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"534e849a83a4819291159aab4e3d274b8e96153f","tid":221580,"uid":12941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:01:11.000Z","msg":"頭先沖完涼喺屋企R頭<br />\n忽然R到舊垃圾<br />\n諗住掃走佢點知佢喺頭頂跌落嚟嘅時候見到粒野飛開左<br />\n一搵原來係佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq0W963.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq0W963.jpg&h=15289812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我住中層<br />\n今日都只係去過市區<br />\n究竟佢邊度嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0fdd40ee5633d72c9fdd9e71e92d876d40a738","tid":221580,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:11:41.000Z","msg":"爬下又比風吹下咁上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw拎出去放生啦唔識養唔好亂養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1201b3319e657b9e57fd7440ef01179e4a9eea","tid":221580,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:13:53.000Z","msg":"風景爸打要負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bd7dd2be634c78ee72f4d7f68f91ee71f07aed","tid":221580,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:16:23.000Z","msg":"養啦"},{"pid":"2c1dba2a64f90cff19a1dd66a9111ebe38869619","tid":221580,"uid":12941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爬下又比風吹下咁上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw拎出去放生啦唔識養唔好亂養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁細隻放生會唔會生存唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907f283d9202b555f27798d960c8340fe28a0001","tid":221580,"uid":12941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"捉左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y04Yv4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy04Yv4w.jpg&h=2c3d07a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cec7e32cff75d055cea1abddb821458cdcfb0bcf","tid":221580,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"螳螂係肉食昆蟲 如果你要養要捉其他昆蟲俾佢食 果蠅、飛蛾之類<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者去金魚街買細果隻麥皮蟲俾佢食<br />\n同埋要俾水份佢 用水壼噴少少水係容器壁到<br />\n不過野生既最好放生佢啦 欣賞一陣好喇"},{"pid":"0d32cdde41f092ec175aa2c0eb407ec055968f73","tid":221580,"uid":12941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57349Ps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57349Ps.jpg&h=3faed7eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉左隻生蚊滋仔俾佢但佢好似唔係好郁<br />\n<br />\n陣間出街就放生佢"},{"pid":"1921e6c0af63f7a3f1b7a8c7dc341d549016ce8d","tid":221580,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>螳螂係肉食昆蟲 如果你要養要捉其他昆蟲俾佢食 果蠅、飛蛾之類<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者去金魚街買細果隻麥皮蟲俾佢食<br />\n同埋要俾水份佢 用水壼噴少少水係容器壁到<br />\n不過野生既最好放生佢啦 欣賞一陣好喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食蟋蟀啦，麥皮蟲又肥又冇乜營養"}]}